Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1

Works like a charm. Without this patch the KeyError is raised if we got defined tags in metadef json file in such manner:

"tags": [
  {"name": "database"},
  {"name": "software"}
]

Besides that, method _get_resource_id compares third argument (resource_name) against name column, so that's illogical to provide tag ID in this place.
